OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FYorkshire Arriva bus       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdrivers strike in row over 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fpay                        
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Arriva buses across parts of Yorkshire 
OL,6, have been suspended due to drivers     
OL,7, going on strike in a pay dispute.      
OL,9,FThe industrial action by Unite members 
OL,10,Fstarted at 02:00 BST and is to last for
OL,11,F"for an undisclosed period of time".   
OL,13,FPhil Bown, from the union, apologised  
OL,14,Ffor the disruption to passengers but   
OL,15,Fsaid workers wanted an                 
OL,16,F"inflation-related pay increase of     
OL,17,Faround 10%".                           
OL,19,FArriva said its offer was a            
OL,20,F"significant increase" and described   
OL,21,Fthe strike action as "unjustified".    
